Package com.iopipe.plugin.trace

This contains the trace plugin implementation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TraceExecution
    This is the trace plugin which is used to track specific marks and measure performance.
    TraceMeasurement
    This class measures a duration of time and is intended to be used with try-with-resources to measure how long a given block of code takes to execute.
    TracePlugin
    This is the trace plugin which is used to track specific marks and measure performance.
    TraceUtils
    This is a convenience class which contains static methods for creating marks and measurements without needing to obtain the instance of the tracing plugin execution state and performing executions on that.
